            <category>
                <![CDATA[嬰兒牀]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285341</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>德國科技企業 Bosch 在 CES 2025 展會中展示全新 AI 智能嬰兒牀「Revol」，內置多重感應器，能即時追蹤及監測嬰兒的心率、呼吸頻率與周圍環境數據，為父母提供詳細報告及即時提醒，冀能減少育兒焦慮。目前這款產品暫未公佈確實推出日期，Bosch 計劃 2026 年於中國市場率先發售，稍後才登陸美國市場。</p><h3></h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285346" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/d4fc6cc0cbd511efaa7f-1-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/d4fc6cc0cbd511efaa7f-1-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/d4fc6cc0cbd511efaa7f-1.jpeg 960w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Revol 嬰兒牀外觀與現有智能嬰兒牀 Snoo 相似，採用透氣網狀牆壁設計，並具備自動搖動功能。Revol 創新引入垂直升降搖動模式，牀墊會模仿升降機緩慢上升及下降，進一步舒緩嬰兒情緒。此外 Revol 配備內建視像監控系統，能向父母提供實時影像畫面。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285366 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010641132-694x424.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="424" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010641132-694x424.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010641132.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>牀架上延伸出的手臂內藏多組感應器，可監測嬰兒周邊環境，包括温度、濕度及空氣質素等數據。當中使用毫米波雷達感應技術，能精準測量嬰兒心率及呼吸頻率，並將數據同步至家長手機應用程式，實現隨時隨地掌握健康報告的需求。</p><h3></h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285347" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ebe332b0cbd611efbfff-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ebe332b0cbd611efbfff-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ebe332b0cbd611efbfff.jpeg 960w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>作為 2025 年新產品，Revol 亦具備 AI 技術，透過電腦視覺檢測嬰兒身邊是否有毯子或毛絨玩具等物件靠近臉部，並即時發出安全提醒，減少意外窒息風險，呼應美國兒科學會對嬰兒睡眠環境安全的建議。</p><h3></h3><p>Bosch 表示，Revol 售價預計約 1,200 美元（約港幣 HK$9,360），還會推出多款配件，如可將嬰兒牀轉換成尿布更換台或書桌，延長產品使用壽命。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_33883"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YeqqxAyYQm8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/smart-home/boschs-ai-enabled-bassinet-tracks-everything-youd-ever-want-to-know-about-your-babys-sleep-025258549.html">Engadget</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
