            <title>【CES 2025】Samsung 全新 AI 驅動電視亮相  Neo QLED 8K + 無線連接 + AI 實時字幕</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/samsung-ai-tv-2025/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-ai-tv-2025</link>
